        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-250" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-250" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Yes &#8211; I&#8217;ve been working with Forbes since the acquisition. </p>
<p>And, true, not all of our journalists moved with us. True/Slant was their site, they wrote about their own topics (with guidance as requested and needed). So there were many topics &#8211; many slants &#8211; not all of which made sense for Forbes&#8217; narrower needs. </p>
