        <div id="dsq-comment-body-235" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-235" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>The journalists should never have felt that they were building our brand instead of theirs &#8211; our mistake. If I were to do it again, I&#8217;m not sure we&#8217;d even have a newstilt.com site and brand.</p>
