            <div id="dsq-comment-message-224" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Your credentials to run a news organization: &#8220;I&#8217;m a compiler geek, with a slant towards scripting languages. I work on the Javascript team at Mozilla. Before that I did a PhD in compiler optimizations, static analysis and scripting languages.&#8221;</p>
